The &#39;default&#39; job configuration included with H3 is the best starting 
model; we suggest starting with it and making small changes, testing 
them one at time, until you&#39;re comfortable with the Spring XML 
(crawler-beans.cxml) format.

At the bottom of the &#39;default&#39; job/profile page, you can clone the 
configuration to another configuration to customize and launch. (A 
&#39;profile&#39; can only be &#39;built&#39; for testing, but not launched.)

- Gordon @ IA

